= Increase our Influence

As a major political force in the country, we have the power to influence certain factions. We should take this towards our advantage.

Where do we increase our influence?

- @usp_reform: In the USP reformist faction.
- @centre_judges: In the centrist wing of the Supreme Court.
- @oligarchs: In the Oligarchs and the Lotherberg Group.
- @easy_discard
- @cancel_advisor_action

@usp_reform
subtitle: -1 resource.
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
choose-if: resources >= 1
on-arrival: resources -= 1; clavin_influence += 1

We increase our influence over Clavin and his fellow party members, which might prove advantageous in controlling the USP from within and with constitutional reforms.


@centre_judges
subtitle: -1 resource.
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
